s of the vertex\np-Laplacian and the edge $p^*$-Laplacian of a graph. We also apply the theory\nto Cheeger inequalities and $p$-Laplacians on oriented hypergraphs and\nsimplicial complexes. Also, the first nonlinear analog of Huang's approach for\nhypergraphs is provided.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Jun 2021 05:43:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 7 Sep 2021 07:10:28 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 24 Nov 2021 06:14:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-25"}
